{"tid":337159,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司徒華樂觀面對末期肺癌","createTime":"2017-07-27T05:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T02:04:26.000Z","uid":49279,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c427071a2352b60d4cb7ff1e0c1f7d4be2ab102","tid":337159,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"何俊仁患病其間親身出席民主活動，過往有不少民主派人士患病其間積極參與民主運動。其中已故支聯會主席司徒華2010年確診罹患第四期腺性肺癌，當時癌細胞已擴散到骨頭，無法治癒，只能靠藥物控制病情。當時華叔的主診醫生莫樹錦形容，華叔勇敢、樂觀面對癌病。<br />\n<br />\n而華叔與癌魔抗戰期間，雖然要接受化療等，但在最後的日子，華叔仍心繫教育及民主發展，千叮萬囑接班人要做好教協及支聯會工作。<br />\n<br />\n前公民黨黨魁及主席、資深大律師余若薇2007年證實患有俗稱「血管瘤」的腦部動脈腫瘤，當年她因長期頭痛，經磁力共振及斷層掃描結果證實在於鼻骨附近，發現一個3毫米大的血管瘤。其血管瘤位置在鼻骨附近，若進行手術難度甚高，當時其夫曾勸她減少工作壓力，以穩定血壓減低血管瘤爆破風險。"},{"pid":"71075bc618df4df61435825024423c8966614a0f","tid":337159,"uid":28155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"點解你咁快死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條屍都火化埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想binc 都唔得"},{"pid":"5f6244512b65a10b169f7a3e773d9e15f67a0cad","tid":337159,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c138e641f985ea4c995d39925f4bfaf987b8ff4","tid":337159,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T05:40:19.000Z","msg":"食屎啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"2b3ea3d951f354e6c74459d4be0942419d9e437d","tid":337159,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T02:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食屎啦屌你老母</block